Los Angeles Clippers | Company Profile, Marketing Contacts, Media Spend, Brands

Los Angeles Clippers are a professional basketball team based in Los Angeles, CA. They play in the National Basketball Association (NBA) and are members of the NBA Western Conference's Pacific Division. The franchise started as the Buffalo Braves in 1970, became the San Diego Clippers in 1978, and then moved to Los Angeles.
